      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SPARBER-James N. Bernstein. Died suddenly on May 27, 1998. Adored son of Gloria Bernstein Sparber and the late Dr. Joseph Bernstein. Most beloved brother of Jody Sparber Giordano and Francesca Sparber Harvey. Beloved uncle of four. Precious and darling sweetheart of Joyce Jaffe, always and forever.</p>
